name: retrieve_proxy_information
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool proxy_checker.
Tool description: An easy tool to test proxy whether it's online, anonymous, is it HTTP, HTTPS or both, to get proxy performance timings.
API description: For retrieving a proxy test result, you should make a request to this endpoint.

is_id.description: **User Request ID** - received from the response of sending a proxy for checking.
